featured_reviews.review_id:
The Mastan Baba dargah in Kowkoor attracts people not just from the city but from neighbouring districts as well. Established in 1974 by an ex-serviceman Syed Ahmed Hussain, the dargah became popular as people believe their wishes come true.

The dargah is located right in front of the Qutb Shahi Mosque showcasing the strong belief of people who visit this place to get relief from their problems.
